<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Cocleare Drake'sBane</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-07-03 21:25:40</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Salutations,<BR>
I aquired this staffa t lvl 29 or so.  It was only doable with the help of a lvl 50 Necromancer(IRL Friend).<BR>
The rods are in the following locations<BR>
Lake rathe--under the 3bird island<BR>
HighKeep--under a waterfall<BR>
Neriak Foreign Quarter(NeriakB)--Outside the Blind Fish Bar<BR>
Dagnor's Cauldron--Steraight out and right from the KK ent.<BR>
Unrest--Opposite the Gnomish Spelunker<BR>
EverFrost--Under the river, follow the right wall to a house<BR>
Qeynos Catacombs--In the Shark Room.. wander around<BR>
Oasis of Marr--Underwater tower near Spec. tower<BR>
Lower Guk-- This is an easy one, in the Hand room, the     Lord group kills it, so just ask and they'll let ya grab it<BR>
<BR>
Erud Crossing--This is the big momma, this rod is the one that keeps anyone without a LOT of VERY big friends from getting this staff.  The last rod is guarded by SIX lvl 45 Killer Sharks.  Last time I checked, the Sharks see through all invis.. not sure about invisibility to animal.. but I wouldnt count on it.  The Sharks aggro everything,, including eachother.  I got the rod before there were 6, there used to be 3, and 2 would fight and while they are fighting you swim down.  But,, cant do that now.. You're gonna have to wait unless you're in an Uber Guild =) Sorry all ya baby Wizards hehe<BR>
<BR>
Cocleare Drake'sBane<BR>
46th Circle DarkElf Arcane Warrior(Wizard)<BR>
~*~Immortal Circle~*~</font></td></tr></table>
